dct_title_s: New map of the Puget Sound country
dct_description_sm: compliments of Pacific Realty Co. ; Franklin Co., Engravers Chicago.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights; depths by bathymetric soundings.
Shows topography, drainage, vegetation, counties, cities, railways, mineral resources, glaciers.
"A valuable compendium of useful information and complete railway and navigation guide for travelers and settlers."
